Serves powers and antenna angles to LabView

THING.text: NOTE: if you 'restart_all' on the rvp8, Rvp8Driver cannot reconnect to^NL^the time-series API. A reboot of rvp8 is reqired.^NL^This is not normal. We need to investigate why this is happening.

Notes:^NL^(a) sunscan and vert data are written^NL^automatically when the antenna scans the sun^NL^or points vertically.time series archive is not scrubbed.^NL^(b) 'save' data are written whenever a trigger file exists.^NL^This file is created and destroyed by scripts.
